com.saic.uicds.core.infrastructure.endpoint
Class DirectoryServiceEndpoint

java.lang.Object
  com.saic.uicds.core.infrastructure.endpoint.DirectoryServiceEndpoint
All Implemented Interfaces:
com.saic.uicds.core.infrastructure.util.ServiceNamespaces
@Endpoint
public class DirectoryServiceEndpoint
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.saic.uicds.core.infrastructure.util.ServiceNamespaces

The Directory Service allows UICDS clients to retrieve information on common data sources, common tools, and services available on this core installation. The following information is available:

  • UICDS Cores that have Information Sharing Agreements
  • Available services
  • Available external tools
  • Available external data sources
  • Available sensor observation services (SOSs)
  • Active incidents (to be deprecated, use Incident Management Service instead)

Since:
1.0
Author:
Aruna Hau
